{"tid":1961760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南亞漢夥兩本地男　劫富士大廈鳳姐逾3萬元財物","createTime":"2020-04-07T04:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T09:19:25.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a80f04c46647e04afb9ff63a3688f073ea1fbdd4","tid":1961760,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zEMZo6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEMZo6o.jpg&h=8d9598b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(7日)凌晨零時14分，一名南亞漢偕同2名本地男子，闖至灣仔駱克道383號鳳樓林立的富士大廈一單位。<br />\n<br />\n據悉當時姓吳(43歲)鳳姐聞門鐘響起，不虞有詐開門之際，南亞漢亮刀指嚇，兩名本地漢並推門而入，搶走女子內藏約25,000港元及4,000元人民幣的銀包，以及2部共值8,000港元的手機，賊人得手後奪門逃去。吳沒有受傷，驚魂甫定後報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報趕至，在附近一帶兜截後惜無發現，同時向女事主了解案發經過，並根據其提供的資料，正追緝兩名本地口罩漢，其中一人約1.75米高，案發時穿短褲、白色膠手套及帽；同時亦追緝一名口罩南亞漢，他案發時穿長袖上衣及長褲。案件列作行劫，交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200407/mobile/bkn-20200407012517399-0407_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200407%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200407012517399-0407_00822_001.html&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2leyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e424a40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200407/mobile/bkn-20200407012517399-0407_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e256458cd340d65dbed6b73cc6c47327aa14257","tid":1961760,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"差佬有無份劫？"},{"pid":"441db14d8fadc5293d1a633e634910989ad91eab","tid":1961760,"uid":89868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"43歲鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9039289daffb4e23aae25ddbc6a884aafa99757d","tid":1961760,"uid":199602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e256458cd340d65dbed6b73cc6c47327aa14257","tid":1961760,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04